-- Novagalicia Seeks 8 Billion Euros to Boost Capital, Cinco Says
-- B y   E s t e b a n   D u a r t e
-- 2012-05-24T05:47:02Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-05-24/novagalicia-seeks-8-billion-euros-to-boost-capital-cinco-says.html
Novagalicia Banco is seeking to raise
8 billion euros ($10 billion) to boost its equity, Cinco Dias
reported, citing unidentified people familiar with the matter.  About 75 percent of the amount may come from public funds
and the remainder from private investors, the newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Esteban Duarte in Madrid at 
